These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: funk, r&b, reggae, folk, country, hip-hop, punk
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
4. the fan of country is between the fan of funk and the fan of reggae##2
5. the fan of folk is between the fan of r&b and the fan of funk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | punk | reggae | country | funk | folk | r&b | hip-hop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: photography, sudoku, drawing, card-games, rock-climbing, video-games, writing
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is photography##2
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | video-games | writing | photography | drawing | card-games | sudoku | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
