5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | singing | reading | chess | puzzles | rock-climbing | camping | video-games |

